                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840915-49-off241 t17840915-49-cd242"></join>, thirty-eight yards of sail cloth, value 34 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17840915-49-victim593" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Adams
                  <interp inst="t17840915-49-victim593" type="surname" value="Adams"></interp>
